A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the life and memory of Mr. Abit Massey; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Mr. Abit Massey served this state for many years with honor and distinction as
3 President and President Emeritus of the Georgia Poultry Federation; and
4 WHEREAS, Mr. Abit Massey served on numerous boards and commissions across our great
5 state; and
6 WHEREAS, Mr. Abit Massey graduated from the University of Georgia with a degree in
7 Business Administration and from Emory University with a law degree; and
8 WHEREAS, he was united in love and marriage to his wife, Kayanne, and was blessed with
9 two remarkable children, Lewis and Camille, and four wonderful grandchildren, Chandler,
10 Cameryn, Christian, and Lucia Kai; and
11 WHEREAS, a man of deep and abiding faith, Mr. Abit Massey served for many years as a
12 Deacon at the First Baptist Church in Gainesville, Georgia; and
