13 WHEREAS, Congressman Buddy Carter recently introduced a bill in the United States
14 House of Representatives to name the USDA National Poultry Research Center in Athens
15 after Mr. Abit Massey; and
16 WHEREAS, Mr. Abit Massey spent many joyful and successful days at the State Capitol
17 lobbying on behalf of the poultry industry; and
18 WHEREAS, a Celebration of Life attended by hundreds of people took place in July to honor
19 the life of Mr. Abit Massey.
20 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
21 join in honoring the life and memory of Mr. Abit Massey and express their deepest and most
22 sincere regret on his passing.
23 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
24 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the family of Mr.
25 Abit Massey.
